{"tid":1550182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關自殺數量好似急升既誤解","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:37:02.000Z","uid":2734,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"179c6623a04ba8dd02e1a8fc7e6c9b9af531482d","tid":1550182,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"利申返先 我唔係話自殺呢d野係少事 但大家唔好無限放大 好似呢排真係多左好多咁<br />\n<br />\n高登有人整理左全年既事件 其實同平時係差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=59d18b67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a>"},{"pid":"d2c9bc0245ec6f92de358187bd70444ae66ed318","tid":1550182,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2728c9a060e8dc870a5d48e045fc1a44c3ef2de","tid":1550182,"uid":78267,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"最近關心咗所以睇落多咗？"},{"pid":"901a592a953fe09b33ead40d81ae1a2ba32ab98f","tid":1550182,"uid":22447